edu.umn.cs.spatialHadoop.nasa

Class HTTPInputStream

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.io.InputStream
      • edu.umn.cs.spatialHadoop.nasa.HTTPInputStream
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Closeable, AutoCloseable, org.apache.hadoop.fs.PositionedReadable, org.apache.hadoop.fs.Seekable

    public class HTTPInputStream
extends InputStream
implements org.apache.hadoop.fs.Seekable, org.apache.hadoop.fs.PositionedReadable
    A wrapper around a stream obtained from URL.openStream() that makes it Seekable and PositionedReadable to be used with FSDataInputStream, hence HTTPFileSystem. All methods are delegated to the underlying (wrapped) input stream. Non-supported methods raise an exception if called.
    Author:
    Ahmed Eldawy
